<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Prag</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Auskunft über die angebliche Gefangenschaft Konrad Möstels, Bürger zu Nürnberg.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_248" id="124r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_248_r2l1">Der Gröſſern Stat cʒu Prag </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_248_r2l3"><expan>Lıeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan> Vns hat ~ des Conrad Möſtels eliche vvirtin fürbraht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r2l4">vvie Jr <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Conrad Möſtell Jren elichen vvirte gefangen habt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r2l7">Biten vvir ewr <expan>erſ<ex>amkeit</ex></expan> <expan>fleiſſiklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_248_line_1576666446085_8573">ob dem alſo ſey </ab></add> daʒ Jr vns 
<add><ab facs="#facs_248_line_1576666449598_8578"><expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab></add> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wiſſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r2l8">laſſen wöllet vmb waʒ ſache Jr Jn gefangen habt / vnd wie </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r2l9">Er das verſchuldet hab . Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_248" id="124r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Der grössern stat czu Prag </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, uns hat des Conrad Möstels eliche wirtin
                        fürbraht, wie ir <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Conrad Möstell, iren
                        elichen wirte, gefangen habt, biten wir ewr
                            <expan>ers<ex>amkeit</ex></expan>
<expan>fleissiklich<ex>e</ex>n,</expan>
<add>ob dem also sey,</add> daz ir uns
                            <add><expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan></add>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wissen lassen wöllet, umb waz
                        sache ir in gefangen habt und wie er das verschuldet hab. Das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
